quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,"Gees-taab ne arzεgse n liib yãmba n mɑɑn-y soɑglɑ."
  102,2,"Hal tɩ y wa tʋg n kaag yaado."
  102,3,"Pa woto ye! Y na wa n bãnge!"
  102,4,"Rẽ poorẽ pa woto ye! Y na wa n bãnge!"
  102,5,"Pa woto ye! Yãmb sã n da mii bãng-n-wãaka, (y kõon n mɑɑn soɑgl ne rẽ ye)."
  102,6,"Lak y na yã Gεhɩɩmã."
  102,7,"Rẽ poorẽ, lakɩ y na yã-a ne nif vẽenega."
  102,8,"Rẽ poorẽ b na sok yãmba, raar-n-kãngã, neemã wã yelle."
